# - Find MySQL
# Find the MySQL includes and client library
# This module defines
#  MYSQL_INCLUDE_DIR, where to find mysql.h
#  MYSQL_LIBRARIES, the libraries needed to use MySQL.
#  MYSQL_FOUND, If false, do not try to use MySQL.
